Extension : OWRobotsTxt v0.1beta
Requires : eZ Publish 4.x.x (not tested on 3.X)
Author : Open Wide <http://www.openwide.fr>

Installation:
------------
- Copy owrobotstxt in extension directory and activate it.
- Clear cache : php bin/php/ezcache --clear-all
- Regenerate autoloads : php bin/php/ezpgenerateautoloads.php -e
- Create the content class robots_txt :

* Name : robots.txt
* Identifier : robots_txt
* Object name pattern : robots.txt
* Attributes :
1 - Identifier : production
    Data type : eztext
2 - Identifier : other
    Data type : eztext

Note : if you are using owmigration extension, you can create the content class with the file owmigration/owrobotstxtmigration.php.

Usage
------------
See README for details